name: The Three Door Corinthia Sideboard
description: The elegance of the three door Corinthia side cabinet will transform any room finished in a beautiful combination of contrasting high gloss and satin option timbers carefully selected by the Davidson design team to complement each other perfectly. The outer case can be finished in any of DAVIDSON's smart timber finishes. The radial pattern that bursts across the three doors shows the capabilities of British craftsmanship which has been hand made to stunning effect. The three door Corinthia is on push latches create a smooth flush front raised on chic legs offering a lighter look option to some of the heavier designs from the collection.
